== Get the sources: ==

git clone git://git.code.sf.net/p/deepmethod/code deepmethod-code

To update the source tree to the latest you'll need to:

cd deep
git pull

== Prerequisites: ==

glib-2.0 >= 2.22
gthread-2.0 >= 2.22
gio-2.0 >= 2.22

== Build: ==

cd deep
autoreconf -fi
./configure --prefix=/usr/local
make
su -c 'make install'

mackoel@gmail.com

